Six seasons. Sharing the story of a brave, beautiful Black family for this window of time is an honor. Much love to our mighty crew and cast. Much love to our people in Louisiana going through a tough time right now. Much love to all who watch and embrace the journey of The Bordelons. They return September 7, proudly on the Black woman-owned and Black woman-led cable network, @owntv. xo 

